Resource.Name: Action List Extension
Resource.Description: Action List Extension adds a customizable report to the interface that allows the display and manipulation of multiple items from one location.

Resource.Name: Transition Icon
Resource.Description: This Form Extension adds an icon to a transition form that allows the user to quickly identify the current application in use.

Resource.Name: Expand All
Resource.Description: This Form Extension adds a dropdown menu to a transition form that allows the user to quickly expand certain or all expanders. When an option is selected, the user will also be redirected to the particular expander chosen.

Field.Name: Item Id
Field.Description: The displayed identifier of the item

Field.Name: Tag/Label
Field.Description: Optional categorical words to be applied to the CR record, for later use by the product team

Field.Name: Submitter
Field.Description: The person who created/submitted the item

Field.Name: Submit Date
Field.Description: The date that the item was created/submitted

Field.Name: Submitting Agent
Field.Description: The person who submitted the item, even if submitted on behalf of another.

Field.Name: Last State Change Date
Field.Description: The last time the state of this item was changed

Field.Name: Close Date
Field.Description: The date that the item was closed

Field.Name: Active/Inactive
Field.Description: Whether the item is active or inactive in its current state

Field.Name: Project
Field.Description: The project in which this item resides

Field.Name: State
Field.Description: The current state of the item

Field.Name: Owner
Field.Description: The primary person who currently owns the item

Field.Name: Secondary Owner
Field.Description: The secondary people who currently own the item

Field.Name: Last Modified Date
Field.Description: The last time the item's data was changed

Field.Name: Last Modifier
Field.Description: The last person to change the data in this item

Field.Name: Last State Changer
Field.Description: The last person to change the state of this item
